strings.Value: "Vordakai filled a sepulcher – a place of peace and contemplation – with passion and pointless vanity. I found it… disturbing."
"For once we think alike — Vordakai got what he deserved!"
"And we kicked his ass. Damn, we're good!"
"Well, it's his sepulcher. Anyone is free to do whatever they wish in their own house. – Even if they're dead!"
